      "title": "Sri Lanka shares slip in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka shares slipped for the second consecutive session on Monday (25), Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index fell 0.40 per cent or 30.51 points to 7,691.27 at 1130 hours.",
        "The most liquid index slipped 0.06 percent or 1.44 points to 2,460.54."
